# Patterns the api-watchdog looks for on each role's tmux pane to flag
# transient, retryable Anthropic API / network errors. One extended regex per
# line; case-insensitive. Edit freely; per-clone, gitignored if you wish.
API Error.*Rate limit
API Error.*temporarily limiting requests
API Error.*Overloaded
rate.*limited
Connection error
Network error
ECONNRESET
ETIMEDOUT
fetch failed
socket hang up
